Likewise, if it is indeed verified, but (the difference) when added to genus does not produce species, since it is evident that this would not be the specific difference of genus, as every specific difference united with genus produces species;
but if this be not the difference, neither will that which was mentioned, since it is divided oppositely to this.
Moreover (he errs), if he divides genus by no,­ gation, as those who define a line to be length without breadth, since this signifies nothing else than that it has no breadth ;
